Print a glmsusie Model Summary

Source: R/method.R
print.summary.glmsusie.Rd

Print a glmsusie Model Summary

Usage

# S3 method for class 'summary.glmsusie'
print(x, digits = max(3, getOption("digits") - 3), max_sets = 5, ...)

Arguments

x

A summary.glmsusie object created by summary.glmsusie().

digits

Number of significant digits to use for printing.

max_sets

Maximum number of confidence sets to display (default: 5).

...

Additional arguments (not used).

Value

The summary object invisibly.
